## Implementation Plan: `@prisma/generator-rest-client`

### 1. Overview

This package is an **external Prisma generator** that reads the DMMF (Data Model Meta Format) provided by the Prisma engine and outputs a single `rest-client.ts` file containing typed TypeScript interfaces and a REST API client class hierarchy. It follows the JSON-RPC protocol implemented by `generatorHandler` from `@prisma/generator-helper`.

